      • SCUIXAPINameValueInputParam

        public SCUIXAPINameValueInputParam(java.lang.String param,
                                   java.lang.String nsIdentifier,
                                   java.lang.String pathSeparator,
                                   java.lang.String pathSeparatorRegex)
        Public constructor. Construction expects parmeter name as input. Parameter name should be in expected format. If not, validParam flag will be set to false.
        Expected Parameter name format: <nsIdentifier><namespace>:<path_delimited_by_pathSeparatorRegex> param Parameter Name nsIdentifier Namespace Identifier. If passed as null, it will be defaulted to "ns:". pathSeparator Path Separator. If passed as null, it will be defaulted to ".". pathSeparatorRegex Path Separator Regular Expression. If passed as null, it will be defaulted to "//.".
